author: henripetrow
body:
#### PR description: 

This PR adds the v0.0.0 Level-1 Trigger SeededCone 8 2-Prong Jet Model to CMSSW. This model tags seededcone 8 jets with 2-prong score. 


The model is documented [here](https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1--baTZ7vc-vcKdcNATrpA78QbN899LJCU1e3WlJQNAU/edit?pli=1&slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199#slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1--baTZ7vc-vcKdcNATrpA78QbN899LJCU1e3WlJQNAU/edit?pli=1&slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199#slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199). 

 
This PR includes changes to the jet data format tag scores by adding a 2-prong score. 


The cms-hls4ml model file tagged v0.0.0 is found [here](https://github.com/cms-hls4ml/L1TSC82ProngJetModel/releases/tag/v0.0.0)  
 

This PR relies on an addition to the cms-dist externals, with the open PR [here](https://github.com/cms-sw/cmsdist/pull/10337) . 

 

#### PR validation: 

 The testing and the performance of the model is presented [here](https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1--baTZ7vc-vcKdcNATrpA78QbN899LJCU1e3WlJQNAU/edit?pli=1&slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199#slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199https://docs.google.com/presentation/d/1--baTZ7vc-vcKdcNATrpA78QbN899LJCU1e3WlJQNAU/edit?pli=1&slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199#slide=id.g381caaa0472_0_199).
title: [L1T] L1TSC82ProngJetModel (Phase 2)
